doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='Medet Ahmetson thoughts')
        meta(name='author', content='Medet Ahmetson (https://turkmenson.com)')

        title Medet Ahmetson blog

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.3/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora:400,700,400italic,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body
        header.container
            .row
                .col-lg-12.col-md-12.mx-auto
                    .site-heading.text-left.masthead
                        h2 Medet Ahmetson blog!
                        p.subheading Also known as Turkmenson. Thoughts, ideas and values to share your worries give to him
        hr
        // Main Content
        .container
            .row
                .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12.mx-auto
                    .site-heading.text-left.masthead
                        p
                            | Medet, you believe in Eternal!
                            | All your worries give to him.
                            | Forgive people, be in the mood of vernal
                            | And he will take you out from grim!
                .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-12.mx-auto
                    .site-heading.text-left.masthead
                        p
                            | Praise the Lord, mention him in this times
                            | Don't be scared that you believe in god!
                            | If people are annoyed, it won't hurt you
                            | With this idea, let's start this blog!
            .row
                .col-lg-4.col-md-4.mx-auto
                    a(href="eternal-talk.html").btn.btn-primary.text-left
                        h3.post-title
                            | God and me
                        p.post-subtitle
                            | All my thoughts, my worries I share with God
                .col-lg-4.col-md-4.mx-auto
                    a(href="projects-for-people.html").btn.btn-primary.text-left
                        h3.post-title
                            | People and me
                        p.post-subtitle
                            | Improving life of all humanity
                .col-lg-4.col-md-4.mx-auto
                    a(href="blockchain.html").btn.btn-primary.text-left
                        h3.post-title
                            | Me
                        p.post-subtitle
                            | Some interesting notes or research reports
        hr
        // Footer
        hr
        footer
            .container
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.col-md-10.mx-auto
                        ul.list-inline.text-center
                            li.list-inline-item
                                a(href='https://twitter.com/AhmetsonMedet')
                                    span.fa-stack.fa-lg
                                        i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                                        i.fab.fa-twitter.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                            li.list-inline-item
                                a(href='https://www.facebook.com/medet.atabayev')
                                    span.fa-stack.fa-lg
                                        i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                                        i.fab.fa-facebook-f.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                            li.list-inline-item
                                a(href='https://github.com/ahmetson')
                                    span.fa-stack.fa-lg
                                        i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                                        i.fab.fa-github.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                        p.copyright.text-muted.text-right by Medet Ahmetson
                        p.copyright.text-muted.text-right 14 May 2021

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js')
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
